!item [Description:]
The (!nolink [XBIOS]) function VgetSize returns the size of the 
screen buffer in bytes for the graphic mode (!I)mode(!i).

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function returns the size of the screen buffer in bytes.

!item [Availability:]
